1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to motor vehicles; to amend sections 18-1736,
2 37-1278.01, 60-376, 60-378, 60-3,167, 60-479, 60-4,112, 60-4,114,
3 60-4,114.01, 60-4,118.01, 60-4,121, 60-529, 60-6,340, 60-1901, and
4 60-1902, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, sections 60-3,135.01,
5 60-3,221, and 60-4,122, Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement,
6 2024, and sections 28-306, 60-301, 60-302, 60-386, 60-3,100,
7 60-3,104, and 60-3,163.02, Revised Statutes Supplement, 2025; to
8 change provisions relating to the use of designated parking spaces
9 for handicapped or disabled persons; to change suspension of
10 operator's licenses to revocation of operator's licenses relating to
11 certain judgments of conviction; to change provisions relating to
12 bonded certificates of title for motorboats; to define a term; to
13 change and provide provisions relating to In Transits, transporter
14 license plates, applications for registration under the Motor
15 Vehicle Registration Act, and the display of license plates; to end
16 the issuance of special interest motor vehicle license plates as
17 prescribed; to provide for Choice Color Plates as a type of
18 alternate license plate; to recodify provisions relating to military
19 service applicable to certain persons as applicable to any
20 operator's license; to change and provide provisions under the Motor
21 Vehicle Operator's License Act relating to certain examinations and
22 to the renewal of certain licenses by qualified licensees; to change
23 provisions relating to proof of financial responsibility; to
